description: The fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing primarily in domestic equity securities of any market capitalization and U.S. Treasuries through other unaffiliated ETFs (including leveraged ETFs and inverse ETFs). The adviser allocates the fund's assets equally between two proprietary investment models. The adviser's first investment model identifies trends in the equity markets. The adviser's second investment model uses two sub-strategies.
name: FormulaFolios Hedged Growth ETF
